e.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aHagiographie. 4aMärtyrertum. 4aSpätantike. 7aRELIGION / Christianity / History.2bisacsh  aHagiography.  aLate Antiquity.  aMartyrdom.1 aGemeinhardt, Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLeemans, Johan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Theology and Religious Studies 2000-2014 (EN)z978311023854908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Theology and Religious Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110638165oZDB-23-GTR08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE THEOLOGY, JUDAISM, RELIGION 2012z978311029384508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET THEOLOGIE,RELIGIONSWISS., JUDAISTIK 2012z9783110288957oZDB-23-DGF0 cprintz978311026351040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110263527zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110263527zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110263527/original  a978-3-11-023854-9 DGBA Backlist Theology and Religious Studies 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0 DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-029384-5 E-BOOK PACKAGE THEOLOGY, JUDAISM, RELIGION 2012b2012  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGFb2012  aZDB-23-DGGb2012  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-GTRc2000d2014